---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Who we are and why we do this.">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-display font-semibold mb-12">About</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-brand-gray-700">
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We're <strong>Result Marketing</strong> — a Malaysian company obsessed with helping SMEs grow through smart marketing and automation.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black mt-12 mb-4">Why this site exists</h2>
        <p>
          We spend a lot of time learning from the world's best business minds — Jay Abraham, Alex Hormozi, Sam Parr, and others who've built and scaled real businesses.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most of their advice is aimed at the US market. We take those insights and translate them for Malaysian SMEs. Different culture, different challenges, same principles.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black mt-12 mb-4">What we believe</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><strong>Evidence over trends.</strong> We value knowledge that's stood the test of time. Large data sets. Peer-reviewed studies. Things that actually work.</li>
          <li><strong>First principles thinking.</strong> We solve problems based on fundamental truths, not just copying what others do.</li>
          <li><strong>Hypothesis → Test → Result → Iterate.</strong> The scientific method applied to business.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black mt-12 mb-4">Our services</h2>
        <p>
          We run an SEO agency at <a href="https://seo.resultmarketing.asia" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">seo.resultmarketing.asia</a>. But this site isn't about selling. It's about sharing what we learn.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you want to chat about how these ideas apply to your business, <a href="https://cal.com/zen-pdcnlc/coffee" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">book a free call</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black mt-12 mb-4">Who's behind this</h2>
        <p>
          Jacob Ng runs Result Marketing from Malaysia. He helps clients with SEO and automation, and spends way too much time watching business podcasts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
